OOC: Works for me.

::Ender::
       The blast from Rodimus's rocket was far enough away from him that it 
only knocked him over, since he was quite a distance from Proto at the time.  
He picked himself up and dusted himself off.  "Oh wait.  You shot me."  He 
frowns.  "Now what am I going to do with you?"  He shakes his head and sighs. 
 "Ah yes, I'll kill you."  He smiles and fires four shots at Rodimus's head.

--part1_d2.1a777c9d.2a55334a_boundary
